sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant API as Flask API
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant EMB as Embedding Model
    participant FA as FAISS Index

    U->>UI: Fill bug form / upload file
    UI->>API: POST /submit-bug (JSON)
    API->>DB: INSERT into bugs
    API->>EMB: encode(title + description)
    EMB-->>API: 384-d vector
    API->>FA: search(top_k=5)
    FA-->>API: [(kb_id, score)]
    API->>DB: SELECT knowledge_base WHERE kb_id IN (...)
    DB-->>API: KB rows
    API-->>UI: {bug_id, similar_bugs[]}
    UI-->>U: Render Top-5 cards + refresh stats
